to jump in after. But Donald had said in that thread, one of the biggest barriers I face in

00:34:08.560 --> 00:34:14.159
building dashboards or packages is convincing people that the work is worth the maintenance

00:34:14.159 --> 00:34:19.679
costs from either my team or theirs and would love additional discussions around this. Any

00:34:19.679 --> 00:34:20.399
thoughts you have?

